        <abstract>
            <para>The imaging of the Herbarium of Tula Museum (TKM) is under the joint grant 19-44-710002 r_a &amp;#34;Assessment of the diversity and visualization of the flora of the Tula region using modern information technologies&amp;#34; (supervisor T.Yu. Svetasheva, TulSPU). Scans of this herbarium are available on the Moscow Digital Herbarium (https://plant.depo.msu.ru/) as a separate collection. According to the project, it is planned to digitize five Tula regional herbaria.</para>
        </abstract>
